Subprog AS_SEZCOD(VALEUR)
Variable Char    VALEUR()
Local Integer INDIC : INDIC = indice
Raz mkstat
Call TITADI(GBOUT1,"11674") From TRTDIV
Call TEXTE(6028,GBOUTS) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(12276,GBOUTP) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(16134,GBOUTA) From OBJDIV
Onkey 129 Titled GBOUT1 Call B1_SEZCOD(zc) From W1CPYLEGKSA
Onkey   2 Titled GBOUTS Call S_SEZCOD(zc) From W1CPYLEGKSA
Onkey 144 Titled GBOUTP Call P_SEZCOD(zc) From W1CPYLEGKSA
Onkey 146 Titled GBOUTA Call SA_SEZCOD(zc) From W1CPYLEGKSA
